        protected IMergeViewer.MergeViewerSide computeSide(IMergeViewer.MergeViewerSide side)
        Returns the correctly mirrored side for this viewer based on the current mirrored state. If this viewer is not mirrored, the side is returned as is, otherwise its opposite site is returned.

        Returns:
